          <h3 class="text-secondary">Portfolio</h3>
          <h2 class="mb-3">Web Projects</h2>
          <hr class= "half-line">
      </div>
      <div class="row no-gutters">
        <a class="col-lg-6 col-xl-5", id="pawsome-card" href="http://www.pawsome.org.uk", target="_blank">
          <div class="">
            <div class="caption">
              <span class="pawsome">
                <div class="h2">Pawsome</div>
                <p class="mb-0">Built over two weeks as part of a team at Le Wagon, this app
                  encourages ethical adoption by helping users
                  find their perfect pets, with animals from mulitple adoption centres. Features include a custom matching
                  system and a real-time chatroom.
                </p>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a class="col-lg-6 col-xl-5", id="bathroom-card" href="https://protected-dawn-08992.herokuapp.com", target="_blank">
          <div class="">
            <div class="caption">
              <span class="bathroom">
                <div class="h2">BorrowMyBathroom</div>
                <p class="mb-0">Initially made as an Airbnb clone within a team of three, this app showcases a mapbox, search feature,
                and slick CSS to help you find a book a bathroom in London.
                <br></p>
              </span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
      <a class="btn btn-dark btn-xl js-scroll-trigger mt-5" href="#arduino">Arduino Projects</a>
    </div>
  </section>
